  "title": "Store Operations Manager #81759",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Manufacturing/ Food Production</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Store Operations Manager</strong></li><li>Working Location: Senoko</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days (Mon – Fri, 8am – 5pm; Sat, 8am – 12pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic $7,000 - $8,000 + Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Manage and oversee daily operations across 8 restaurants.</li><li>Lead and guide outlet operations to meet agreed targets and support ongoing improvements.</li><li>Support business growth, including planning and setting up new outlets in Singapore or nearby countries.</li><li>Implement cost control and cost-saving measures.</li><li>Plan staffing needs, including recruitment, training, staff development, motivation, deployment, reassignment, and handling workplace issues to ensure effective use of manpower.</li><li>Carry out other duties or projects assigned by the Director.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>At least 5 years of relevant experience in F&B operations, preferably managing multiple outlets (e.g., casual dining or hotpot).</li><li>Strong leadership, communication, and interpersonal skills.</li><li>Working knowledge of Microsoft Office is required.</li><li>Proficient in English; ability to communicate with Mandarin-speaking stakeholders for work purposes is an advantage.</li><li>Able to work on Saturdays.</li><li>Willing to travel when required.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#81759 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
